First have a linux virtual machine setup in your local using virtual box or vmware
After you have the Linux Virtual Machine do the following:
1. Setup docker - https://docs.docker.com/install/linux/docker-ce - choose based on your Linux OS
2. Setup IBMCloud CLI - https://cloud.ibm.com/docs/cli?topic=cloud-cli-getting-started -
3. Setup IBMCloud CR CLI - https://cloud.ibm.com/docs/container-registry-cli-plugin?topic=container-registry-cli-plugin-containerregcli
4. Setup OCP CLI - https://cloud.ibm.com/docs/openshift?topic=openshift-openshift-cli
